# Modular Codebase Enhancements for Future Upgrades

This implementation plan covers structural changes to ensure TrackPrep is modular enough to easily adopt Redis caching (Phase 2), Socket.io real-time updates (Phase 3), complete Dockerization including Redis (Phase 4), and various analytical or scheduling features (Phase 5) without needing modifications to core controllers or schemas later.

