### Docker & Config (Phase 4)

#### [MODIFY] [docker-compose.yml](file:///C:/Users/anshu/OneDrive/Desktop/TrackPrep/docker-compose.yml)
Add a standard `redis:7-alpine` container configuration alongside `db`, `server`, and `client`. Pass `REDIS_HOST=redis` and `REDIS_PORT=6379` env configurations to the backend service.

