### Background Scheduling & Analytical Features (Phase 5 Skeletons)

#### [NEW] [emailService.js](file:///C:/Users/anshu/OneDrive/Desktop/TrackPrep/server/src/services/emailService.js)
A helper class using `nodemailer` (if installed) or logging mail payloads directly to stdout in dev modes.

#### [NEW] [jobService.js](file:///C:/Users/anshu/OneDrive/Desktop/TrackPrep/server/src/services/jobService.js)
Uses `node-cron` (dynamically imported) or a `setInterval` fallback to structure cron schedules for weekly reports and daily email reminders for pending tasks. Started at `index.js` bootstrap and cleaned up on shutdown.

#### [NEW] [githubService.js](file:///C:/Users/anshu/OneDrive/Desktop/TrackPrep/server/src/services/githubService.js)
A modular integration API service using `axios` to query profile details or repository commits for profile integrations.

#### [NEW] [pdfService.js](file:///C:/Users/anshu/OneDrive/Desktop/TrackPrep/server/src/services/pdfService.js)
A PDF exporter wrapper utilizing `pdfkit` (dynamically imported) or returning structured text summaries in a buffer fallback, ready for use.

